</p><p>The motivation and development of this expression for <i>category utility</i>, and the role of the multiplicand <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \textstyle {\tfrac {1}{p}}}">
