</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Information-theoretic_definition_of_the_Category_Utility">Information-theoretic definition of the Category Utility</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Category_utility&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: Information-theoretic definition of the Category Utility">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>The <a href="/wiki/Information-theoretic" class="mw-redirect" title="Information-theoretic">information-theoretic</a> definition of <i>category utility</i>  for a set of entities with size-<span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle n\ }">
