</p><p>The intuition behind the above expression is as follows: The term  <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle p(c)\textstyle \sum _{i=1}^{n}p(f_{i}|c)\log p(f_{i}|c)}">
