<p>If we will rewrite the original <a href="/wiki/Category_utility#Definition_of_the_Category_Utility" title="Category utility">definition of the category utility</a> from above, with <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle C=\{c,{\bar {c}}\}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>C</mi>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mo fence="false" stretchy="false">{</mo>
        <mi>c</mi>
        <mo>,</mo>
        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mover>
              <mi>c</mi>
