            </mrow>
          </munder>
        </mstyle>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \textstyle \sum _{f_{i}\in F}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/97b6713e37292c74ac79bfc2a0eee8a91ca66d2d" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.338ex; width:6.444ex; height:3.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \textstyle \sum _{f_{i}\in F}}"/></span> in the <i>category utility</i> equation  runs over independent binary variables <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle F=\{f_{i}\},\ i=1\ldots n}">
